      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/swiss-central-bank-calls-more-action-capital-regulation-2024-03-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士国家银行周二呼吁对银行资本监管进行审查，称瑞士需要制定规则，承认瑞银集团在收购瑞士信贷银行后已成为一家更具系统重要性的银行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/swiss-central-bank-calls-more-action-capital-regulation-2024-03-19/</guid>
