      <title>联合利华剥离冰淇淋部门 裁员 7,500 人以节省成本</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/unilever-spin-off-ben-jerrys-unit-launches-cost-savings-plan-2024-03-19/</link>
