      <title>日本央行放弃激进政策 17 年来首次加息</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japan-poised-end-negative-rates-closing-era-radical-policy-2024-03-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行结束了长达八年的负利率和其他非正统政策的残余，实现了历史性转变，不再试图通过数十年的大规模货币刺激来提振经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japan-poised-end-negative-rates-closing-era-radical-policy-2024-03-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 22:13:04 GMT</pubDate>
